'''Art Parkinson''' (born October 19, 2001) is an Irish actor, based in [[Wikipedia: Moville|Moville]], [[Wikipedia: County Donegal|County Donegal]]. He played the role of 'Young Kenneth' in the movie ''[[Wikipedia:Freakdog|Freakdog]]'' (also called ''Red Mist'' in some territories). Parkinson has also appeared in the Irish horror film ''[[Wikipedia: Dark Touch|Dark Touch]]'' as &quot;Peter&quot;. He has also acted in several school productions and commercials. His mother Movania Parkinson is an Irish actress and runs a drama school. Parkinson also has two older brothers named Pearce and Padhraig, who have also appeared in several British and Irish television productions.&lt;ref name=&quot;Derry Journal 5 April 2014&quot;&gt;[http://www.derryjournal.com/what-s-on/cinema/game-of-thrones-art-parkinson-taking-movie-and-television-worlds-by-storm-1-5982625 Game of Thrones Art Parkinson taking movie and television worlds by storm]&lt;/ref&gt;

In ''[[Game of Thrones]]'', he plays the role of [[Rickon Stark]]. He was announced in the role on 29 September 2010. He initially appeared as a guest star in the [[Season 1|first season]] and returned in this role for the [[Season 2|second]] and [[Season 3|third]] seasons. He did not appear in the [[Season 4|fourth season]]. More recently, Parkinson has played the role of 'Ingeras', son of [[Wikipedia: Dracula|Dracula]], in the 2014 movie ''[[Wikipedia: Dracula Untold|Dracula Untold]]'' alongside fellow Game of Thrones actors [[Charles Dance]] and [[Paul Kaye]].&lt;ref&gt;[http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/les-miserables-game-thrones-actors-594166 'Les Miserables,' 'Game of Thrones' Actors Join Universal's 'Dracula' (Exclusive)]&lt;/ref&gt;

Art Parkinson has also been cast in the action film ''[[Wikipedia: San Andreas (film)|San Andreas]]'' as Ollie, a ten-year old boy caught in the middle of a massive earthquake in California.&lt;ref name=&quot;Derry Journal 5 April 2014&quot; /&gt; On October 6, 2014, Art confirmed that his character and [[Natalia Tena]]'s character [[Osha]] would not be returning for the [[Season 5|Fifth Season]]. During an interview with Flicks and the City, Parkinson also mentioned that he was not allowed by his parents to watch ''Game of Thrones'' due to its R18 content apart from a few scenes that were related to him.&lt;ref&gt;[http://winteriscoming.net/2014/10/06/art-parkinson-confirms-rickon-osha-still-awol/ Art Parkinson Confirms Rickon, Osha Still AWOL]&lt;/ref&gt;

His mother Movania Parkinson helped Art to secure the role of Rickon Stark after learning from a friend that the casting team had been unable to find someone to play that character. After doing a screen test, Art met the producers and the voice coach [[Brendan Gunn]], who got him to repeat the same test. As a result, Art was picked for the role of Rickon.&lt;ref name=&quot;Derry Journal 5 April 2014&quot; /&gt;
